com.eyecall.connection

Class OutQueue<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eyecall.connection.OutQueue<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - Object type to be sent across the socket

    public class OutQueue<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    Buffers <E>'s to be sent across a Socket. When this Runnable is fired up, it will send messages added to the queue. The objects will be serialized to JSON prior te being sent. Adding messages to this queue is thread safe.
    Author:
    Nicker
